rComments: Outstanding professor and person. I took Dr. Fisher for two classes during my Master's Degree program. Her readings complimented the course and its objectives; she makes you a better writer, communicator, class facilitator, and critical thinker; and she cares about her work, her class, and her students. You will not regret taking her classes!

Super good professor. She's very kind, understands the course material very well, can explain any difficulties you're having quite clearly, and isn't a very hard marker provided you show some effort and understanding of the course material. 10/10 would enroll again
